  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1037190/extras/e19d5c39ae30449a610dd3fae8855e7d.poster.avif?t=1726860941\" width=770 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1037190/extras/e19d5c39ae30449a610dd3fae8855e7d.webm?t=1726860941\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1037190/extras/e19d5c39ae30449a610dd3fae8855e7d.mp4?t=1726860941\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Shipped is a simple local multiplayer naval game for up to 8 players. You can accelerate, but you can't brake! Grab crates to get ammunition or shoot air with your empty cannons to push enemies or deflect incoming fire. Keep up with the movement of the camera! If your ship goes off-screen it will instantly explode!<br><br>Shipped includes a single-player arcade mode and 50 time-trial challenges.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Local multiplayer for 2-8 players.<br></li><li>Play with friends or against the AI.<br></li><li>5 different game modes.<br></li><li>Single-player challenges.<br></li><li>Compatible with Steam Remote Play Together.</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1037190/extras/e19d5c39ae30449a610dd3fae8855e7d.poster.avif?t=1726860941\" width=770 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1037190/extras/e19d5c39ae30449a610dd3fae8855e7d.webm?t=1726860941\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1037190/extras/e19d5c39ae30449a610dd3fae8855e7d.mp4?t=1726860941\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Shipped is a simple local multiplayer naval game for up to 8 players. You can accelerate, but you can't brake! Grab crates to get ammunition or shoot air with your empty cannons to push enemies or deflect incoming fire. Keep up with the movement of the camera! If your ship goes off-screen it will instantly explode!<br><br>Shipped includes a single-player arcade mode and 50 time-trial challenges.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Local multiplayer for 2-8 players.<br></li><li>Play with friends or against the AI.<br></li><li>5 different game modes.<br></li><li>Single-player challenges.<br></li><li>Compatible with Steam Remote Play Together.</li></ul>",
